{"tid":2374473,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"泫雅要回歸啦！新專輯收錄與男友 DAWN 的合作曲","createTime":"2021-01-21T08:53:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T09:37:28.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"05e11385854d48b933c67dbd30f46601c271f68b","tid":2374473,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T08:53:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_d0bbef740dbc6c97615f8676744ef0a0/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-21/133166-894287.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_d0bbef740dbc6c97615f8676744ef0a0%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-21%2F133166-894287.png&h=ea05816a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n時隔將近三年半，泫雅終於將再度發行迷你專輯，先來看看她會發表哪些歌曲吧！<br />\n<br />\nP Nation 今天（21 日）公開了泫新第七張個人迷你專輯〈I&rsquo;m Not Cool〉的概念照，華麗的背景和裝扮襯托著泫雅自由奔放的表情，展現出強烈的視覺效果。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_c5558b44c1c6c8c9431c9ff7f0115aaf/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-21/133166-894288.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_c5558b44c1c6c8c9431c9ff7f0115aaf%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-21%2F133166-894288.jpg&h=871a4129&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_a513f1dbc161a53fc45b1ce62ad16547/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-21/133166-894293.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_a513f1dbc161a53fc45b1ce62ad16547%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-21%2F133166-894293.jpg&h=4262f6d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〈I&rsquo;m Not Cool〉將以同名主打歌為首，收錄 &ldquo;GOOD GIRL、&ldquo;Show Window&rdquo;、和男友 DAWN 合作的 &ldquo;Party, Feel, Love&rdquo;，還有泫雅於 2019 年加入 P Nation 後首度推出的單曲 &ldquo;FLOWER SHOWER&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n泫雅將於 1 月 28 日帶著〈I&rsquo;m Not Cool〉回歸，喜歡她的話最近別忘了鎖定各種預告啊！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YZl5xfq2-pk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYZl5xfq2-pk&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcIbCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=f07cd4be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YZl5xfq2-pk</a>"},{"pid":"4c41b031cb04ad00ffa49b01812b41f121ada637","tid":2374473,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T08:55:11.000Z","msg":"上好電<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出場"},{"pid":"b7f28381eda6140c735623ab44d27750f9b16868","tid":2374473,"uid":181448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:00:31.000Z","msg":"又話出正規<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前Good Girl 應該拍左Mv 唔知遲d 會唔會都打歌呢"},{"pid":"defe076c1310fc715633df341422e546708712a2","tid":2374473,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:37:28.000Z","msg":"瘦版渡邊直美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}